Description: The cost of living is drastically rising. According to CNBC, wage growth has been consistent with an inflation rate of 4.5% while many consumer prices have increased by 9.1%. Americans are feeling the brunt of inflation especially at the grocery stores, gas stations, and with rent payments. This results in more citizens being on government assistance programs like food stamps or Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP).
William Peace University was founded in 1857. It's motto is Esse quam videri - "To be, rather than to seem".

Chapter: North Carolina State University At Raleigh
Description: North Carolina State University is located in Raleigh, North Carolina                                        It is know widely as a strong STEM institution. NC State was founded 1887.
